Invocation Name: flatter me
des: Introducing "Flatter Me" Skill, your daily dose of positivity and self-confidence. This skill offers you a selection of compliments that are tailored to make you feel good about yourself, boost your self-esteem, and help you start your day with a positive attitude. Whether you're in need of a quick pick-me-up or just want to remind yourself of your own worth, Flatter Me skill has got you covered. With a new set of compliments offered daily, you can use this skill every day to uplift your mood and feel good about yourself. Enable the skill now and let us help you boost your confidence and feel fabulous!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
